ActCanadian Human Rights Act
PrecisRe-appointment of KAREN ANN JENSEN of Ottawa, Ontario, as a full-time member of the Canadian Human Rights Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term ending on the earlier of October 1, 2022, or the day on which section 419 of the Budget Implementation Act, 2018, No. 2 comes into force, effective October 1, 2020; and her appointment as the Pay Equity Commissioner of the Canadian Human Rights Commission, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, effective on the day on which section 419 of the Budget Implementation Act, 2018, No. 2 comes into force.
